{"tid":7721,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【短片】【紅隧口血人】停車讓路捲入血案 司機車CAM證無辜","createTime":"2016-11-28T03:16:44.000Z","updateTime":"2016-11-28T06:00:32.000Z","uid":18279,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"f2de1bff872d8ec3646299e3d1369157fb99dad4","tid":7721,"uid":18279,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-28T03:16:44.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://hkm.appledaily.com/detail.php?issue=20161128&amp;guid=55974742&amp;category_guid=10829391&amp;category=instant\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhkm.appledaily.com%2Fdetail.php%3Fissue%3D20161128%26guid%3D55974742%26category_guid%3D10829391%26category%3Dinstant&d=O%2B%2FmjTQdNMYEhUtediYwEsW%2Flfx08C7TTpsJ%2BRLLqlo%3D&h=89f0d7e8\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhkm.appledaily.com%2Fdetail.php%3Fissue%3D20161128%26guid%3D55974742%26category_guid%3D10829391%26category%3Dinstant&h=028f48c4\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://hkm.appledaily.com/detail.php?issue=20161128&amp;guid=55974742&amp;category_guid=10829391&amp;category=instant</a><br />\n<br />\n灣仔鴻興道澳洲遊客遇襲案，昨晚，警方到場後，在紅磡海底隧道截獲一部私家車，一度懷疑私家車撞倒遊客後不顧而去，幸好私家車上裝有行車記錄儀，終證實無辜。司機寄語各位車主加裝車行車紀錄儀保障自身。<br />\n<br />\n司機陳生載同女友，準備過海食消夜，駛經海隧灣仔入口前，一名受傷衫上染滿鮮血外籍男子，突走出路中央，站在陳生私家車前，打量幾秒後離開，陳生一度欲落車協助，外籍男子衫袋內插有一罐紅牛，由於他狀似醉酒，加上尾隨車輛響號，陳生遂開車過海，但在收費亭前被隧道公司職員截停，要求等待警員到場調查，警員到場一度懷疑陳涉及意外危險駕駛後不顧而去，幸陳立刻播放「車CAM」記錄證明無辜，而隧道公司閉路電視亦清楚拍下過程，證實不涉及事件，個多小時後，始獲釋開車離開。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4b9426d1ba6607edd113dc8d4698fe459d7cf323","tid":7721,"uid":408,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-28T03:21:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a565356d4544b4698f64333d86b3eac7578d723e","tid":7721,"uid":430,"like